### [2 Chronicles Chapter 22](../../../bib/kjv/ch2022.htm#001.md)

[2 Chronicles](../../../bib/kjv/ch2001.htm#001.md)

<span class="margnote"><span id="an_000">ch2 22:0</span></span>

Overview

[Ch2 22:1](../../../bib/kjv/ch2022.htm#001.md), Ahaziah succeeding, reigns
wickedly; [Ch2 22:5](../../../bib/kjv/ch2022.htm#005.md), In his
confederacy with Joram, the son of Ahab, he is slain by Jehu; [Ch2
22:10](../../../bib/kjv/ch2022.htm#010.md), Athaliah, destroying all the
seed royal, save Joash, whom Jehoshabeath his aunt hid, usurps the
kingdom.

